'''戈格里亞勒'''是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]西北部的小鎮，由[[瓦拉布省|瓦拉布省]]負責管轄，毗鄰與[[蘇丹|蘇丹]][[阿卜耶伊|阿卜耶伊]]接壤的邊界，位於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]西北約700公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Gogrial%20(Bahr%20al%20Ghazal%20Wilayat)&toplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&fromlat=8.5333333&tolat=4.872006&fromlng=28.1166667&tolng=31.601117 |title=Map Showing Juba And Gogrial With Distance Marker |accessdate=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172929/http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Gogrial%20(Bahr%20al%20Ghazal%20Wilayat)&toplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&fromlat=8.5333333&tolat=4.872006&fromlng=28.1166667&tolng=31.601117 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[朱爾河|朱爾河]]流經該鎮[[中心商務區|中心商務區]]以東約5公里處。2011年7月，該鎮中心方圓7公里人口約44,600<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fallingrain.com/world/SU/32/Gogrial.html |title=Estimated Population In 2011 |access-date=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605171716/http://www.fallingrain.com/world/SU/32/Gogrial.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

